videos.description: Nathan Cottrell rushes for a 69-yard gain into the red zone.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Cottrell breaks free for 69-yard run

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall rushes for a 3-yard touchdown to give the Yellow Jackets a lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Marshall's TD run puts Georgia Tech ahead

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall sneaks into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown to extend the Yellow Jackets lead.
videos.headline: Marshall 2-for-2 on Georgia Tech TDs

videos.description: Travon McMillian returns Brenton King's kick off for 70 yards.
videos.headline: McMillian's huge kick off return sets up Virginia Tech

videos.description: Sean Savoy cuts through defenders for a 14-yard touchdown to close the gap on the Yellow Jackets.
videos.headline: Savoy rushes for Virginia Tech's first TD of the game

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall finds Brad Stewart for a 60-yard touchdown to extend the Yellow Jackets lead.
videos.headline: Stewart wide open for a huge Georgia Tech TD

videos.description: Josh Jackson tosses it up, it is tipped by Georgia Tech and caught by Virginia Tech's Eric Kumah for 26 yards.
videos.headline: Two Georgia Tech defenders can't make easy interception

videos.description: Jalen Holston runs for an 8-yard touchdown late in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Holston closes gap for Virginia Tech

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall's pass is intercepted by Greg Stroman and returned for a Hokies touchdown to give them the lead.
videos.headline: Stroman's huge pick-six puts Virginia Tech ahead

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall connects with Ricky Jeune who is wide open down the middle for 80 yards into the end zone to give the Yellow Jackets the lead.
videos.headline: Marshall finds Jeune for 80-yard Georgia Tech TD

videos.description: On fourth down, Josh Jackson chucks it to Cam Phillips in the end zone which is broken up by Ajani Kerr to lead Georgia Tech to a 28-22 victory over Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech stops Virginia Tech on 4th down for the win
